    "Ruckman, Dr. Peter S_": "The `[group_Word_Luk_1]` verse also likens Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` Christ to sunlight, for the only light that would give light to every man on earth would come from the sun; even the stars are called \u201csuns\u201d in the observatories. Furthermore, ONE light is mentioned: \u201cthe TRUE Light.\u201d This would be like the \u201cgreater\u201d light of Genesis 1:16\u2013\n11. Every news media sinner in the list I gave reversed this so that \u201ctheir kind\u201d appear as wonderful, good, kindly people who had come up from animals or (if they had been \u201ccreated in God\u2019s image\u201d) they were STILL in God\u2019s image since nothing went wrong between Genesis 1:27 and Genesis\n11. The verse also likens Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` Christ to sunlight, for the only light that would give light to every man on earth would come from the sun; even the stars are called \u201csuns\u201d in the observatories. Furthermore, ONE light is mentioned: \u201cthe TRUE Light.\u201d This [v_Gen_1_16] would be like the \u201cgreater\u201d light of Genesis 1:16\u2013\n11. Every news media sinner in the list I gave reversed this so that \u201ctheir kind\u201d appear as wonderful, good, kindly people who had come up from animals or (if they had been \u201ccreated in God\u2019s image\u201d) they were STILL in God\u2019s image since nothing went wrong [v_Gen_1_27] between Genesis 1:27 and Genesis",
