    "Warren W. Wiersbe": "). The argument here is from the lesser to the greater. If when we were sinners, God gave us His best, now that we are God\u2019s children, will He not give us all that we need? Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` used this same argument when He tried to convince people that it was foolish to worry and fear. God cares for the birds and sheep, and even for the lilies; surely He will care for you! God is dealing with His own on the basis of Calvary grace, not on the basis of law. God freely gives all things to His own! (3) God has justified us ("
